public class ContingencyImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements Contingency

An implementation of the model object 'Contingency'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Total Islands
  • Outage Branches
  • Monitoring Branches
  • Island Buses
  • Equiv Outage Branches
